reviewText: Both of these films are really good! Richard Dreyfuss is truly a comic genius! The original is the better of the two films, but Rosie is not annoying in the second film and it has some nice homages to the first. I highly recommend this set if you've never seen the movies before
summary: Hilarious! Richard Dreyfuss is spot on perfect!
Title: Stakeout / Another Stakeout

reviewText: Say what you will about production standards, cinematography, directing and so on. Those two movies, seen in order, are just fun. That IS the point to it and that is what they have. A fun evening.
Title: Stakeout / Another Stakeout

reviewText: I loved these movies when I was a kid, and enjoyed them just as much now.  Funny characters getting into nothing but trouble.  The dialog is stellar and with the two disk set you can watch them back to back!
Title: Stakeout / Another Stakeout

reviewText: These movies are hilarious!  My hubby & I have watched them many times & still double over in laughter each time.
Title: Stakeout / Another Stakeout

reviewText: Richard Dreyfuss and Emilio Estevez were great together in both Stakeout movies. These were both action and comedy mixed together.
Title: Stakeout / Another Stakeout

reviewText: I agree with the other reviews. These are very fun and entertaining motion pictures. They never seem to get old! Dreyfuss and Estevez have great chemistry!
summary: Great to add to your collection!
Title: Stakeout / Another Stakeout

reviewText: These movies are very funny, and have casts that would entertain anyone.  We had seen the movies, of course a long time ago, and just decided to purchase them.  We thoroughly enjoyed them, and they are making the rounds now with our kids.  Very funny and clever.  Will watch over and over.
Title: Stakeout / Another Stakeout

reviewText: Took forever for this to arrive and then one disk was bad; seller never acknowledged but Amazon eventually gave a refund.
Title: Stakeout / Another Stakeout
